        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>No Propaganda Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits federal funding of the Corporation for Public Broadcasting. The bill also rescinds unobligated funding made available to the corporation in specified appropriations acts. (The corporation is a congressionally created nonprofit that supports local public television and radio broadcasting.)</p>]]>
        </text>
